@classmethod &amp; @staticmethod If you had the base knowledge in Java, maybe you would have been confused with it.
What is the class method? What is the static method? Are they the same as each other? In Java, the class method does is the static method. They refer to the same thing.
Personally,
@classmethod is the concept of static method(class method) in Java @staticmethod, Without the corresponding concept in Java, it merely belongs to Python. In Python, they are almost identical. Most of the use of @staticmethod can be replaced with @classmethod.
